
https://cordova.apache.org/docs/en/5.0.0/guide/platforms/android/tools.html

Note that plugins can also include build-extras.gradle files via:

<framework src="some.gradle" custom="true" type="gradleReference" />


modelli di plugin per le push:
https://github.com/phonegap/phonegap-plugin-push/


add this in config.xml of your application:

<plugin name="cordova-plugin-settings-hook" spec="~0" />

<platform name="android">
        <preference name="android-applicationName" value="com.buongiorno.newton.cordova.NewtonApplication" />
</platform>